@page "/"

<PageTitle>Signavex</PageTitle>

<h1>Signavex</h1>
<p class="lead">Market discovery and signal analysis tool.</p>

<p>
    Signavex surfaces stocks worth investigating by stacking multiple confirming signals.
    It scans the S&amp;P 500 and S&amp;P 400 universe daily, evaluating technical, fundamental,
    and sentiment indicators against current market conditions.
</p>

<div class="row mt-4">
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">10 Stock Signals</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Technical (MA crossover, support/resistance, trend, channel, volume), fundamental (P/E, D/E, earnings), and sentiment (news, analyst ratings).</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">4 Market Signals</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Market trend, interest rates, VIX fear gauge, and sector momentum gate and scale all stock scores.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Configurable Weights</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Every signal weight is configurable. Stronger macro indicators carry more weight by default.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="mt-4">
    <a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Go to Dashboard</a>
</div>
